animeTitle: Kiki to Lala no Mamatte Suteki!
animeDescription: Lala finds a myserious egg that hatches into a baby dragon who they name Will. She and Kiki try to bring him up but Will grows far too big too fast and uses his dragon instincts which cause a lot of destruction.
